docs.text: Welcome to MkDocs # For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . Commands # mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit. Project layout # mkdocs.yml # The configuration file. docs/ index.md # The documentation homepage. ... # Other markdown pages, images and other files. How to use MkDocs # pip install mkdocs pip install pymdown-extensions pip install mkdocs-literate-nav Then, access to http://127.0.0.1:8000/
